Text:
Track #6, "God Only Knows" is incorrect in this torrent.  It is actually a second instance of Track #7 "They Didn't Believe Me"!  And unfortunately, #6 does not appear elsewhere.

And I hate to gripe more, but...well, the song names are incorrect for much of the bonus disc (CD 2).
And track 9 is a second instance of track 11. Is this down to mischief or incompetence?
